    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主线剧情结束后，瓦哈卡和巴拿马两地仍潜藏着威胁，必须予以平息。每张旧地图都被重新设计，为一场大战做好准备，并融入了一些背景故事。此外，游戏还拥有由 Sonic Kitchen 和 Daniel Estay 创作的 100% 原创配乐。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战地图：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#1：洛玛拉加之战 战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#2：爬行者的狩猎 战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#3：废品场要塞围攻战 战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#4：水坑之火 战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#5：梅布尔的飞升 战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >#6：德州白雪皑皑 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174110/extras/0f064cdbfb6416e03eda1c90e8725612.poster.avif?t=1770320178\" width=1136 height=630 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174110/extras/0f064cdbfb6416e03eda1c90e8725612.webm?t=1770320178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174110/extras/0f064cdbfb6416e03eda1c90e8725612.mp4?t=1770320178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐： Sonic Kitchen, Daniel Estay</p>",
